" VS Code-specific vimrc
" Sources main .vimrc then unmaps keys that VS Code handles via editorScroll

source ~/.vimrc

" Unmap scroll keys - VS Code's editorScroll command is used instead
" (configured in settings.json via vim.normalModeKeyBindingsNonRecursive)
silent! nunmap <C-e>
silent! nunmap <C-y>
silent! vunmap <C-e>
silent! vunmap <C-y>
